  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The hefty beast within clinks its crystalline limbs against the egg.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">placid</span> nature, gentle despite its formidable appearance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>寄宿其中的墩实野兽正用自己的结晶肢体叩击着卵壳。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">平缓</span>的基因潜质，虽然外观给人一种强大的感觉，但其实本性十分温顺。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>裡面的巨獸用水晶般剔透的肢體觸碰蛋殼，發出聲響。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：性情<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">平靜</span>性情，儘管外型嚇人，行為卻十分溫和。"
  },
